name: Metallic Afternoon - Sixth Dream - Part 1
description:
-And what about your wires? -What about them? -Would you like me to draw them as well? -They are a part of me. -I just thought... -Why are you thinking?

The little frog could not find a suitable answer. She continued drawing, even as the lines on her paper kept squirming, dancing, changing with every stroke of her quill.
